products.title: Carlotti Natural Roman Blind
products.description: Dress your windows to impress with the understated elegance of the carlotti natural roman blind. This cotton blind sporting a full poly cotton lining can be raised and lowered with ease to give peaceful shade at any time of day. It is printed with an intricate damask pattern in a cool pastel hue. Product id: db-rom1001 fabric colour: natural material: 100% cotton lining: light filtering poly/cotton blended lining headrail: durable white headrail with top or face fix brackets.
